```

## Benefits

- **Stay in terminal** - No context switching to Linear web app
- **Quick capture** - Create issues in seconds, not minutes
- **Immediate action** - Optionally start work right after creating issue
- **Team visibility** - All work tracked in Linear automatically
- **Rich context** - Claude-generated descriptions are comprehensive
- **Template consistency** - Uses your team's Linear templates

## Configuration

This command uses your Linear workflow configuration:

- **Team**: {{linear.teamName}} ({{linear.teamKey}})
- **Workspace**: {{linear.workspaceName}}
- **Templates**: Fetched from your Linear workspace
- **Default Status**: Issues created as "To Do"

